article_title: ABC's 'NY Med' Hits Ground Running In Second, Post-Obamacare Season

article_metadata.author: Dade Hayes

og.description: ABC's NY Med is a rare broadcast TV summer specimen: a thoughtful and absorbing documentary about intersecting lives inside a major hospital. Executive producer Terence Wrong says the "mini-residency" his production crew completes in filming the show pays off with many genuinely unscripted moments.
